Wellcome May Pull Olympics Bid If Village Not Included, FT Says

-- B y   B l a n c h e   G a t t
-- 
2011-07-03T20:29:50Z

-- http://www.bloomberg.com/news/2011-07-03/wellcome-may-pull-olympics-bid-if-village-not-included-ft-says.html
The Wellcome Trust said it would
retract its 1 billion-pound investment offer for the Olympic
Park in  London  if the government doesn’t include the athletes’
village in the package, the Financial Times reported, citing
Wellcome’s Head of Investment Peter Pereira Gray.  To contact the reporter on this story:
Blanche Gatt in London at 
